{"tid":1627024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《馬其頓人教我地搞「顏色革命」》","createTime":"2019-10-05T14:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:15:10.000Z","uid":300495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35adba84bd7c9a0c33b392c7accd2eb265910dba","tid":1627024,"uid":300495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://medium.com/@hkjohnsonyeung/馬其頓人教我地搞-顏色革命-18174a36efe6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40hkjohnsonyeung%2F%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%B6%E9%A0%93%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%99%E6%88%91%E5%9C%B0%E6%90%9E-%E9%A1%8F%E8%89%B2%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD-18174a36efe6&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=5a244f5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@hkjohnsonyeung/馬其頓人教我地搞-顏色革命-18174a36efe6</a><br />\n「漆彈真係好用，一來成本低，二來法律風險低。我地弄到政府全棟建築物都是顏料，又不是完全毀壞，最多都是罰款。」示威行列中有批「突擊隊」，佢地會攞住裝有顏料的水槍，射向警察和建築物。「是呀，防暴警察拎住真槍著住防暴裝，示威者的突擊隊就打扮到小丑一樣，手中拎住水槍周圍射&hellip;&hellip;你有冇背包式殺蟲水噴射器？農業用品店應該有得賣，可以裝到好多顏料。」"},{"pid":"8930edf486df0420507cd2d2551ccfdfb8843e49","tid":1627024,"uid":123820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}